6:36.000Z","msg":"人要惡過狗<br />\n要比佢知道你係佢主人<br />\n<br />\n每個人教狗都唔同<br />\n我亦唔會批評<br />\n只要狗仔心身唔好受創就可以了<br />\n<br />\n狗仔係唐狗<br />\n識教會好快好聽話"},{"pid":"fc5011f3e03f2c3f241e95bfd56a1a5e4b30b4dc","tid":2499242,"uid":66945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:38:50.000Z","msg":"誰大誰惡誰正確<br />\n你要識喝佢, 下次佢再聽到你喝就會死死氣"},{"pid":"866373a54ef588d4538e14fe5786a3adfdac9961","tid":2499242,"uid":192189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:39:42.000Z","msg":"一咬就一腳踢埋去<br />\n萬試萬靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be3fed55686e97095620d5bb82f618555d62624","tid":2499242,"uid":217222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:04:31.000Z","msg":"去YOUTUBE 睇晒ERIC KO 教狗片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1c09a8049297cd77e6f6a78c3f0a2e1df571d85","tid":2499242,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0be3fed55686e97095620d5bb82f618555d62624","tid":2499242,"uid":217222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:04:31.000Z","msg":"去YOUTUBE 睇晒ERIC KO 教狗片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:11:00.000Z","msg":"唔係惡<br />\n係互相尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ccc93ddb2c61f324abbf7575a5c2c56301a2131","tid":2499242,"uid":15511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"866373a54ef588d4538e14fe5786a3adfdac9961","tid":2499242,"uid":192189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:39:42.000Z","msg":"一咬就一腳踢埋去<br />\n萬試萬靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:11:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f5957b2a40f09589280713